headline: UPS white paper casts shade on e-commerce gig delivery providers
summary: A UPS white paper promotes the benefits of traditional express carriers over gig logistics providers, but the TD Cowen/AFS Logistics Freight Index shows why businesses might like the lower prices from newer last-mile providers. The post UPS white paper casts shade on e-commerce gig delivery providers appeared first on FreightWaves.
